Package hypership

Class Summary
GrapheMembership This class is the connection required for implementing a membership hyperbolic graph representation
GUIFileExplorer This class is the representation of the file system widget.
GUIInfos This class is the information widget on members.
GUIMenu This class is the upper menu bar widget.
GUIOpenGL This class is the OpenGL representation widget.
GUIPopUp Main class for the pop-ups used in the GUI.
GUIPopUpRexec Main class for all the 'rexec' related pop-ups used in the GUI.
GUIPopUpRexit Main class for all the 'rexit' related pop-ups used in the GUI.
GUIPopUpRkill Main class for all the 'rkill' related pop-ups used in the GUI.
GUIProcessManager Main class for the local client for the remote process library.
GUIRps This class is the RPS information widget on processes.
GUIToolbar This class is the main definition of the upper tool bar.
GUITransferable This class implements the transferable functionalities for drag-and-drop.
GUITransferHandler This class is the real transfer handler for drag-and-drop functionalities.
GUIWorkspaces This class only contains the static method for saving or loading a workspace.
Hypership This is the main frame class for the GUI which will contain all widgets.
NodeMembership This class encapsulates the supplementary information about a member for membership purposes.
